hopobject.body: We're at university together cuanto tarda una pastilla de viagra en hacer efecto The 49ers' issues go beyond back-to-back inept performances - the team is under siege for allowing sack specialist Aldon Smith to play in Sunday's game only two days after he was arrested on suspicion of driving under the influence.
